headline: McCormick Declares $0.45 Quarterly Dividend
summary: The Board of Directors of McCormick & Company, Incorporated (NYSE:MKC) declared a quarterly dividend of $0.45 per share on its common stocks, payable October 27, 2025, to shareholders of record October 14, 2025.

headline: Earnings Preview: McCormick (MKC) Q3 Earnings Expected to Decline
